# CTICS Changelog

## v1.0 â€“ August 2025

- Initial public release of the CTICS Manual
- Defined all 5 core levels:
  - 15 Sectors (Level 1)
  - 52 Categories (Level 2)
  - 100+ Niches (Level 3)
  - 190+ Content Styles (Level 4)
  - 60+ Format Types (Level 5)
- Introduced Composite Identifier format: `SS.CC.NN.CS.FT[.III]`
- Published CTICS_ID format spec (regex + schema support)
- Created visual tools:
  - Quick Reference Guide
  - Radial Classification Tree
  - Content Tree Decision Diagram
- Added Metadata schema and implementation notes
- Released under Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 License (CC BY 4.0)

